OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776373859
OL,3,CIsrael and Lebanon leaders to speak as
OL,4,Cmore US troops sent to Middle East
OL,6,FThe leaders of Israel and Lebanon are
OL,7,Fdue to talk, Donald Trump has said, as
OL,8,Fthe US continues to try to find a
OL,9,Fdiplomatic way to end the Iran war.
OL,11,FIn a social media post late on
OL,12,FWednesday, the US president said that
OL,13,Fthe leaders would speak on Thursday in
OL,14,Fa renewed effort to broker a ceasefire
OL,15,Fafter the countries' first direct
OL,16,Ftalks in decades ended the previous
OL,17,Fday in Washington without a deal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776373859
OL,3,CIsrael and Lebanon leaders to speak as
OL,4,Cmore US troops sent to Middle East
OL,6,FOn Truth Social, he said: "Trying to
OL,7,Fget a little breathing room between
OL,8,FIsrael and Lebanon. It has been a long
OL,9,Ftime since the two leaders have
OL,10,Fspoken, like 34 years. It will happen
OL,11,Ftomorrow."
OL,13,FIt was not clear what leaders Trump
OL,14,Fwas referring to.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
