PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776373859
OL,3,CIsrael and Lebanon leaders to speak as
OL,4,Cmore US troops sent to Middle East
OL,6,FThe announcement came as diplomatic
OL,7,Fefforts to end the war continued
OL,8,Facross the Middle East, with leaders
OL,9,Ffrom Pakistan visiting Iran and Saudi
OL,10,FArabia to try to broker an extension
OL,11,Fof the ceasefire.
OL,13,FDespite insisting negotiations were
OL,14,Fongoing, the US has also maintained
OL,15,Fmaximum pressure on the Iranian
OL,16,Fgovernment, with the blockade of its
OL,17,Fcoastline still in force.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
