CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776373859
OL,3,CIsrael and Lebanon leaders to speak as
OL,4,Cmore US troops sent to Middle East
OL,6,FThe US also said late on Wednesday it
OL,7,Fwould send thousands more troops to
OL,8,Fthe region, with 6,000 being sent with
OL,9,Fthe aircraft carrier USS George H.W.
OL,10,FBush.
OL,12,FAnother 4,200 marines were also being
OL,13,Fsent, putting the number of US
OL,14,Fpersonnel involved in operations
OL,15,Fagainst Iran at well over 50,000.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
