OL,3,CIsrael and Lebanon leaders to speak as
OL,4,Cmore US troops sent to Middle East
OL,6,FThe commander of Iran's joint military
OL,7,Fcommand, Ali Abdollahi, threatened to
OL,8,Fhalt trade in the region if the US
OL,9,Fdoes not lift its naval blockade.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
