OL,3,CIsrael and Lebanon leaders to speak as
OL,4,Cmore US troops sent to Middle East
OL,6,FUS Central Command said on Wednesday
OL,7,Fthat no ships had made it past the
OL,8,Fblockade since it was imposed two days
OL,9,Fearlier, while 10 merchant vessels
OL,10,Fcomplied with the direction from US
OL,11,Fforces to turn around and reenter
OL,12,FIranian waters.
OL,14,FThe blockade is intended to pressure
OL,15,FIran, which has exported millions of
OL,16,Fbarrels of oil, mostly to Asia, since
OL,17,Fthe war began February 28. Much of it
OL,18,Fhas likely been carried by so-called
OL,19,Fdark transits that evade sanctions and
OL,20,Foversight, providing cash that's been
OL,21,Fvital to keeping Iran running.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
